  <name>Pohoda Zabbix</name>
  <summary>Zabbix monitoring for Pohoda accounting system</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Business metrics monitoring for the Pohoda accounting system using Zabbix.
       Collects data via shared digest modules through the Pohoda mServer API.</p>
    <p>Monitored metrics include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Debtors count, total amount, and max overdue days</li>
      <li>Waiting income and waiting payments</li>
      <li>Unmatched bank payments</li>
      <li>Invoice and payment counts</li>
      <li>Pohoda mServer connectivity status</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Results are cached for 5 minutes to reduce mServer load.
       Compatible with Zabbix Agent 2 and Zabbix Agent.</p>
  </description>
